longBusinessSummary: Hypebeast Limited, through its subsidiaries, operates as a digital media and e-commerce company in Hong Kong, the People's Republic of China, Japan, the United States, the United Kingdom, and internationally. It operates through Digital Media and E-commerce segments. The company produces and distributes youth focused digital content, which reports the latest trends on fashion, lifestyle, technology, entertainment, culture, and music to its visitors and followers, as well as offers agency services under Hypemaker brand. It also engages in online retail of third-party branded footwear, apparel, and accessories on its e-commerce platform; provision of advertising spaces; and publication of magazines. The company was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Kwai Chung, Hong Kong. Hypebeast Limited is a subsidiary of CORE Capital Group Limited.
